data.description:
Amazing Price. Deals like this will not be around long.  Double Master with full luxury bath including Jutted Tub.  Guest rooms in Guest Wing.  Formal dining and living area, Humongous game room will hold 3 full size gaming tables, upstairs features sound proof music room, storage, a master suite, office, bonus room & balcony.  Full kitchen with yards of counter space and loads of cabinets has informal dining area.  

Neighborhood Description

This is an nice quite neighborhood with good streets
